  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the predictive value of standardized cognitive
      tests performed in health examination centres for the diagnosis of Alzheimer's disease and
      related disorders among adults aged 65 years and older with a subjective memory complaint.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this study is to determine the predictive value of standardized
      cognitive tests performed in health examination centres for the diagnosis of Alzheimer's
      disease and related disorders among adults aged 65 years and older with a subjective memory
      complaint.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
